[div class=p 
	"Powerpig is a homebrew Gameboy Advance platformer. This submission is an improvement to the current movie mainly due to glitch where if you end the current level on a particular frame, the next level will start immediately, as opposed to normally where there is some wait time.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The only requirement to activate the glitch is to end the level on a specific frame, which comes up once every ~10 frames. So it was simply unlucky that Darkman425 never hit the glitch in the numerous levels in the original run.
	$LF
]div
